            </div>
            <div xml:lang="gez" type="edition">
                <note>The full text, based on <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt46">UppEt46</ref>.</note>
                <div type="edition">
                    <ab>
                        በስመ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                        በእንተ፡ ሥራየ፡ ዮኪን፡ ዮፍታሔ፡ ዮፍታሔ፡ ፍታሕ፡ ድድንግኤል፡ ፍታሕ፡ 
                        ክፍትናኤል፡ ፍታሕ፡ እራፎን፡ ፍታሕ፡ እራዛን፡ ፍታሕ፡ አድኅነኒ፡ እምሥራይ፡ 
                        ወእምጸላወጊ፡ ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="translation">
                    <ab>
                        In the name of the Holy Trinity. About the sorcery of Yokin Yoftāḥe. Release Yoftāḥe!
                        Release Dǝdǝngǝʾel! Release Kǝftǝnāʾel! Release ʾƎrāfon! Release ʾƎrāzān!
                        Save me, your maidservant <gap reason="ellipsis"/>, from sorcery and from Ṣǝlāwagi!
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text></TEI>